| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3833 — Mass File Rename (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4ed8b93d-064e-558e-83f2-38aea6782202"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
